org.sxb.session

インタフェース Session

  • 既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    ExpiringSession
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    MapSession

    public interface Session
    Provides a way to identify a user in an agnostic way. This allows the session to be used by an HttpSession, WebSocket Session, or even non web related sessions.
    導入されたバージョン:
    1.0
    作成者:
    Jeffson

    • フィールドの詳細

      • PRINCIPAL_NAME_ATTRIBUTE_NAME

        static final java.lang.String PRINCIPAL_NAME_ATTRIBUTE_NAME

        A common session attribute that contains the current principal name (i.e. username).

        It is the responsibility of the developer to ensure the attribute is populated since Spring Session is not aware of the authentication mechanism being used.

        導入されたバージョン:
        1.1
